    "description": "<p><strong>Style Passive:</strong> You deal +1 damage against creatures that&nbsp;are<strong> Hindered.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Requires: </strong>Attack Check</p>\n<p><strong>Maneuver: (1 AP)</strong> You deal +1 damage, and the target makes a <strong>Physical Save </strong>against being <strong>Hindered </strong>(it has DisADV on Attack Checks and Spell Attacks) on the next Attack Check or Spell Attack it makes before the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>If the target is already <strong>Hindered </strong>then they fall&nbsp;<strong>Prone </strong>instead</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can add Weapon Maneuvers as Weapon Enhacements for easier use. Just press \"Add Martial Maneuvers For Weapon\" on <strong>Enhancements </strong>tab on <strong>Item </strong>sheet.</em></p>",
